---

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>📬 Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>I'm always open to discussing new projects, creative ideas, or opportunities to be part of your vision.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-content">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item glass-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">📧</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Email</h3>
            <a href="mailto:codewithnaman@gmail.com">codewithnaman@gmail.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item glass-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
          <div><h3>Location</h3><p>Bangalore, India</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-social glass-card">
          <h3>🔗 Connect</h3>
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/codewithnaman/" target="_blank" aria-label="LinkedIn">in</a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/codewithnaman" target="_blank" aria-label="Twitter">𝕏</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/codewithnaman" target="_blank" aria-label="GitHub">⌘</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-box glass-card">
        <p>Let's work together to build something great!</p>
        <a href="mailto:codewithnaman@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">Send a Message</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-purple); }
  .contact-content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .contact-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--accent-purple); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.25rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .contact-item h3 { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .contact-item a, .contact-item p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  .contact-social { padding: 1.25rem; }
  .contact-social h3 { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-box { padding: 2rem; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .cta-box p { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .contact-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .cta-box { order: -1; } }
</style>